  "notes": [
    "This case report describes a 36-year-old woman with bilateral breast cancer and a mosaic TP53 pathogenic variant diagnostic for Li-Fraumeni syndrome",
    "The case demonstrates the complexity of interpreting TP53 variants and distinguishing between germline, mosaic, and clonal hematopoiesis origins",
    "Management was significantly altered by the genetic findings, leading to bilateral mastectomy and avoidance of radiation therapy"
  ]
}